{"tid":196360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【買定離手喇喂！】港鐵故障彩 2017 接受投注！","createTime":"2017-04-11T09:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T01:38:23.000Z","uid":29021,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d5ebd7d20d214d2c81a6170389c539b6437b5a6","tid":196360,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港鐵故障彩 2017</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">壞咩綫、點壞法、壞幾鑊，通通有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<strong>競猜一周內列車服務期間的事故類型、涉及行車綫及事故次數，投注項目包括訊號故障、電力故障、出軌、交通意外甚至係罷工！</strong><br />\n<br />\n各位參加者第一次參加嘅時候都會有100分<br />\n而每買一條綫故障／一種故障／每注故障次數競猜就要100分<br />\n買兩條綫／兩種故障就要200分、三條綫／三種故障就要300分......如此類推（故障次數彩除外）<br />\n<br />\n每買中一條綫故障或一種故障類型，彩分就係 (投注額x賠率)<br />\n如果你買咗多於一條綫故障或一種故障類型而全中，賠率仲會乘以你買嘅數目添！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">例如，買將軍澳綫、觀塘綫同東鐵綫，三條綫壞晒，假設賠率都係5，<br />\n彩分就係(100x3x5+100x3x5+100x3x5)=7500<br />\n買訊號故障同電力故障，兩種都中，假設賠率都係5，<br />\n彩分就係(100x2x5+100x2x5)=2000</span><br />\n<br />\n至於買故障次數彩嘅朋友，玩法更簡單：每買中一注，彩分就係 (投注額x賠率)<br />\n誤差1以內，彩分就係 (投注額x賠率x20%)，買0故障而有故障或買有故障而0故障除外<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">例如該期港鐵故障9次，假設賠率係100，<br />\n如果你買咗一注10次或以上，或者一注8次，彩分就係 (100x100x20%)=2000<br />\n如果你買咗一注9次，彩分就係 (100x100)=10000<br />\n買0次故障但最後有1次故障，咁就當唔中</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>另外，負錢嘅朋友，逢星期日會扣5%利息，所以唔好以為擺喺度就算呀，負超過2000就破產架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>仲等？即刻投注啦！</strong></span></span><br />\n投注站：<a href=\"http://goo.gl/JsRlJ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FJsRlJ0&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=c587a6b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/JsRlJ0</a>（於11/4/2017 1800開放）<br />\n賬戶結餘：<a href=\"http://goo.gl/9gzk6n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F9gzk6n&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=79d349c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/9gzk6n</a><br />\n即時賠率：<a href=\"http://goo.gl/gfn32p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fgfn32p&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5ea829c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/gfn32p</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>條款及細則</strong>節錄：<br />\n<br />\n1. 投注時間截至逢星期日港鐵列車服務完結前1日（即星期一凌晨01:30）<br />\n2. 每期由逢星期一列車服務開始起至逢星期日列車服務完結為止（即逢星期一早上05:28至下星期一凌晨01:30）<br />\n3. 如該期開始日或結束日及截止投注日提供通宵列車服務，該期結束日或截止投注日的時間為早上04:59，該期開始日則為早上05:00<br />\n4. 如該期開始日的列車服務提早開始，該期開始日的開始時間則為該日列車服務開始的時間<br />\n5. 如該期結束日及截止投注日的列車服務延長，該期結束時間及截止投注時間則為該日列車服務結束的時間<br />\n6. 以下事故以MTR 、 MTR Service Update 或 傳媒即時新聞公佈為準：<br />\n<ul>[*]訊號故障<br />\n[*]列車／巴士故障<br />\n[*]電力故障<br />\n[*]土木結構損壞<br />\n[*]月台門故障<br />\n[*]發生火警／水浸<br />\n[*]出軌／纜車車廂脫落<br />\n[*]因人手不足或按章工作造成服務受阻<br />\n[*]如行車綫上發現異物導致服務受阻，包括任何生物<br />\n[*]城際直通車因香港一方問題造成服務受阻，會視為東鐵綫服務受阻（如「九廣通」機車故障；不包括「九廣通」機車例行檢修或中國一方造成的問題）<br />\n[*]其他發生於行車綫，由非乘客因素導致的故障或阻延（不包括交通意外）</ul><br />\n7. 以下事故必須以MTR 或 MTR Service Update公佈為準：<br />\n<ul>[*]交通意外（只限輕鐵）<br />\n[*]其他對列車服務做成阻延或影響安全的意外情況</ul><br />\n8. 以下事故不會被計算在內：<br />\n<ul>[*]由乘客因素導致的阻延，除非該乘客因素由非乘客因素形成<br />\n[*]因天氣或其他天然災害，導致鐵路服務需作出預防性調整<br />\n[*]因非員工進行抗議或示威行動造成的服務阻延，除非導致任何異物進入行車綫導致服務受阻<br />\n[*]與列車服務或安全無關的事件</ul><br />\n9. 我們與香港鐵路有限公司及MTR Service Update均無直接從屬關係；我們保留最終龍門位置決定權<br />\n<br />\n完整的條款及細則：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1PXYy0sRyRiMcnC3m0tw5iAjyut_rCNVR_DjWgQ2KZHg/pub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1PXYy0sRyRiMcnC3m0tw5iAjyut_rCNVR_DjWgQ2KZHg%2Fpub&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f585d807\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1PXYy0sRyRiMcnC3m0tw5iAjyut_rCNVR_DjWgQ2KZHg/pub</a><br />\n<br />\n（鳴謝MTR Service Update：<a href=\"http://twitter.com/mtrupdate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmtrupdate&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=76655ba3\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/mtrupdate</a>）"},{"pid":"99667002877199a933690aa844ce1a6d3e2a96ae","tid":196360,"uid":27047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627269fcc02abb0c85ae74121a739b5a55a86170","tid":196360,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41d1fb981b197707d0d0eceb8b35a56ea7ea358","tid":196360,"uid":93674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05128945831644d8d1d8b759fb082377c04b6809","tid":196360,"uid":101986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e133032afa61512635d733eb11949d1bd0afe9da","tid":196360,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:05:31.000Z","msg":"留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850b72d149ea12ebb90935d91982e1262a6c2990","tid":196360,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:11:56.000Z","msg":"快啲跟日本整個延遲統計啦"},{"pid":"8a378ce53bf29c009e221b3d34ea299b39724e06","tid":196360,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcc99ef